title.rendered: The Spoiler Corner: Bones, Justified and More!

content.rendered:
Reading Time: < 1 minute

Finally. Following weeks of reruns, a majority of shows return this week and next week with new episodes.

What can we expect from The Vampire Diaries, Bones and other favorites? Our friends at TV Fanatic have the answers. Just follow the links below…

The Vampire Diaries spoilers: David Anders will be reprising his role as John Gilbert, and two characters will be swapping spit.

Bones spoilers: Will Brennan and Booth finally get together? Producers continue to ponder.

Justified spoilers: The FX series returns on February 9. Look who will be hooking up.

Pretty Little Liars spoilers: There’s a major twist ahead, according to one series star.

Glee spoilers: Songs from Justin Bieber, Katy Perry and Michael Jackson are on tap.
